l/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊度見到我問機票啊"},{"pid":"e5c1240bcb069d3a810472e33b11f046782a7fa5","tid":469794,"uid":86764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你係學生，join Chernobyl tour有discount，但要預先同agent講左先<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係學生就最好上佢個網睇，因為好似星期六日係平d（唔係好記得）<br />\n<br />\n暫時網上係有兩間搞Chernobyl tour嘅agent，Google 都揾到<br />\n<br />\n我當時係喺Warsaw 飛Kiev，來回大約千八蚊港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10475da8ea921eedc6c7619c555a04eb2447396a","tid":469794,"uid":28330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:35:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你去長洲把啦<br />\n搵機票咁基本都要問</blockquote><br />\n咁路線有好多，想知大多數係點飛姐。你咪唔好應囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊度見到我問機票啊</blockquote><br />\nSkyscanner<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29719973db6e44dbba72f209d0798c0c4b6c680a","tid":469794,"uid":14566,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:46:54.000Z","msg":"私人包機最快<br />\n我估你連google下都唔得閒，應該秒秒鐘幾百萬上落<br />\n所以真係慳得一秒得一秒"},{"pid":"6b81d8950c49124b3f1fca0c64c1313ef365c1db","tid":469794,"uid":47041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T23:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你去長洲把啦<br />\n搵機票咁基本都要問</blockquote><br />\n咁路線有好多，想知大多數係點飛姐。你咪唔好應囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊度見到我問機票啊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你標題問點飛先最快最抵<br />\n而家問人邊度見到有問機票<br />\n思覺失調？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95f03ef63221562d3df96711e97f29799e633d5","tid":469794,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俄航 莫斯科轉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛機冇得轉，只能轉巴士，火車落去。"},{"pid":"546ba50d1bca0274e0476eaa0d6281831f5bb98b","tid":469794,"uid":4070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:12:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dccf2117c308a7aa800217cd8c3d7923934989f3","tid":469794,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:12:55.000Z","msg":"Air Astana Early Bird<br />\n<br />\n來回 4,200有找。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗經支京。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/081228_c464c8f3839ab9afab1905f7633ba480.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F081228_c464c8f3839ab9afab1905f7633ba480.jpeg&h=7b811860&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82eedf45e4e45a003531044ceeaabe9dd30bffcb","tid":469794,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>俄航 莫斯科轉</blockquote><br />\n俄航要去白俄羅斯轉多程機<br />\n<br />\n都係多哈/哈薩克轉最方便<br />\n<br />\nPlan緊下年去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n白俄，你有澳門護照就得<br />\n<br />\n依家香港白俄仲未有免簽<br />\n<br />\n我驚你機都上唔到。<br />\n<br />\n##新果個白俄免簽5日，係要你喺非俄羅斯機場去，當係國際線入境先可以做。"},{"pid":"2f38acec02a6734d41b7deef5880a4d40d8f0995","tid":469794,"uid":51744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俄航 莫斯科轉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n俄航？  俄烏兩國所有直航全部停飛有一年啦<br />\n<br />\n去基輔最快有兩條航線－1. 北京 － 基輔 或 2. 曼谷 － 基輔，兩條線都係烏航。"},{"pid":"f84aae82e1b26b9f5a0f34197f0adada0cf9814c","tid":469794,"uid":51744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Air Astana Early Bird<br />\n<br />\n來回 4,200有找。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗經支京。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/081228_c464c8f3839ab9afab1905f7633ba480.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F081228_c464c8f3839ab9afab1905f7633ba480.jpeg&h=7b811860&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢條線都順路，都係轉一次機。  <br />\n<br />\n仲有其他選擇嘅：卡塔爾航空／土耳其航空"},{"pid":"f110dfbe9bcccced7b7e5b37daf20113f8a73af0","tid":469794,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Air Astana Early Bird<br />\n<br />\n來回 4,200有找。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗經支京。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/081228_c464c8f3839ab9afab1905f7633ba480.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F081228_c464c8f3839ab9afab1905f7633ba480.jpeg&h=7b811860&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢條線都順路，都係轉一次機。  <br />\n<br />\n仲有其他選擇嘅：卡塔爾航空／土耳其航空</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但 Air Astana 唔係日日有機<br />\n<br />\n同埋我search 呢班去程係要經 ALA 去 TSE 先再上機去 KBP，有一班極短時間轉機，但我可以肯定轉唔到，根本連拎行李都擺唔切。<br />\n<br />\n國際線&gt;&gt;國內線&gt;&gt;國際線<br />\n<br />\n除非夾到來回都係經 ALA 轉 KBP，咁就方便好多。<br />\n<br />\n回程就好啲，直接 ALA 轉機。"},{"pid":"05ae491b9ae4abe624a5a55939c95cef2a8ef82d","tid":469794,"uid":40042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T20:06:16.000Z","msg":"上兩年搭俄航玩俄羅斯+波羅的海三國+烏克蘭<br />\n我係由立陶宛飛基輔 烏克蘭航空 300蚊港紙單程包行李<br />\n開頭諗住玩完基輔搭飛機返莫斯科<br />\n但果陣岩岩講俄烏切斷航空路線 都搞到我頭都大晒<br />\n最後買左烏克蘭國鐵頭等二人房 搭夜行火車返去<br />\n每人盛惠1600港紙<br />\n<br />\n至於Chernobyl tour 我join soloeast <br />\n愈早book愈平"},{"pid":"5b5dc9a394206c6fb12f52b078b7cba0b64f6739","tid":469794,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T00:57:06.000Z","msg":"第一次去好好彩坐歿代CX (S7) 飛莫斯科再轉落基輔<br />\n<br />\n第二次去要由波蘭陸路入，果次無坐俄航。<br />\n<br />\n第三次係俄羅斯陸路入。(其實唔算係去烏克蘭，因為係去頓湼次克。)<br />\n<br />\n出年第四次會由白俄羅斯入，機票都出埋，<br />\n<br />\nMINSK &gt;&gt;&gt; KYIV &gt;&gt;&gt; WARSAW 坐 UIA 全包五百幾蚊港紙。"},{"pid":"e0ff80d5a3b544a4d1eae2b29bbf50f24693fea6","tid":469794,"uid":13129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:24:49.000Z","msg":"記得join 2日1夜<br />\n我參加即日都幾走馬看花"}]}